  left_join(planes, by = "tailnum") %>%
  group_by(carrier) %>%
  summarise(total_planes = n(),

  mutate(missing_pct = not_in_planes / total_planes) %>%

   ~x, ~y,
   1, 1,
   2, 1)

   1, 1,
   1, 2)
